 its resources are spread over all the clients/packages hosted on the server. Shared Hosting is perfect for personal websites, small and mid-sized businesses that do not require all the resources of a server.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Can I host multiple Web sites within one Shared Hosting plan?" tab_id="1597239331336-bd2cd26d-5388"][vc_column_text]Yes! Our Pro and Business shared hosting plans allow you to host more than one Website, by adding secondary domains through your hosting control panel i.e. cPanel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Is there a Money Back Guarantee?" tab_id="1597239518010-6bac6fca-3659"][vc_column_text]Yes, we offer a 100% Risk Free, 30 day Money Back Guarantee.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Is Email hosting included in my package?" tab_id="1597239562564-0f6dac79-f331"][vc_column_text]Yes, all our Hosting packages come with Unlimited Email Hosting.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Can I upgrade to a higher plan?" tab_id="1597239630922-4c2aaf50-a434"][vc_column_text]Yes, you can easily upgrade to one of our higher plans at any time.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Is my data safe? Do you take backups?" tab_id="1597239696297-173ca8ad-d905"][vc_column_text]Yes, your data is a 100% secure and is backed-up every 5 days.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Do you include protection from viruses?" tab_id="1597239736379-3e5d1564-6b0a"][vc_column_text]Yes, all our servers are protected by Clam AV.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Can I divide my Shared Hosting package and resell it?" tab_id="1597239776210-61737821-aea9"][vc_column_text]While a Shared Hosting package cannot be used for this purpose, you can easily resell custom packages with our Reseller Hosting. To view our Reseller Hosting plans, \r\n<a href="https://websitesbymike.net/reseller-hosting.php">click\r\n    here.</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Do you offer SSH access?" tab_id="1597239808400-17650b5c-06fe"][vc_column_text]Yes, we provide SSH access to your domain. Because this is a shared environment, you will not get root access. However, you will be able to achieve most of your requirements by having the rights to access only the files relevant to your domain.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Q. Who do I get in touch with if I need help?" tab_id="1597239842404-4f3de25a-74b9"][vc_column_text]Our Support team is always at hand to assist you. You can take a look at all our contact details \r\n<a href="https://websitesbymike.net/support/contact-us.php">here </a>.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n', 'Linux Shared Hosting', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'linux-shared-hosting', '', '', '2020-08-13 16:53:17', '2020-08-13 16:53:17', '', 119, 'http://redcirclehost.local/?page_id=1051', 0, 'page', '', 0),
