est-performing WordPress sites with our Cloud Hosting. With cache and CDN auto-configured on\r\n                    all your packages, pages load much faster with the least amount of resources.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="block">\r\n            <div class="feature inline-block">\r\n                <span class="wp-host-feature-icon block backup"></span>\r\n                <h3>Auto-Backups</h3>\r\n                <p>Get a time machine for all your WordPress sites. With CodeGuard automatically set up for any site you\r\n                    create, your data is always protected and regularly backed up.</p>\r\n                <span class="inline-block ss-badge">Security Suite</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="feature inline-block last">\r\n                <span class="wp-host-feature-icon block secured"></span>\r\n                <h3>Auto-Secured</h3>\r\n                <p>No need to worry about viruses or hacking attempts. All your WordPress sites will be regularly\r\n                    scanned for malware with SiteLock\'s advanced security tools.</p>\r\n                <span class="inline-block ss-badge">Security Suite</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="container" style="margin-top: 105px;">\r\n    <div class="row">\r\n        [whmpress_pricing_table_group id="5"]\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wp-host-aboutus-wrp">\r\n    <h2>WordPress powers 27% of websites on the Internet</h2>\r\n    Build anything - a blog, a static website or an ecommerce shop\r\n    <div class="wp-host-aboutus-content">\r\n        <ul class="inline-block first">\r\n            <li><span class="block">Ready-made Themes</span>\r\n                Choose from over 25,000+ themes available for any type of business, portfolio, or blog.\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li><span class="block">Diversified Plugins</span>\r\n                Add features to your websites by installing plugins in a few clicks.\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <ul class="inline-block">\r\n            <li><span class="block">SEO-friendly</span>\r\n                With pre-integrated SEO friendly module, drive maximum traffic to your site through search engines.\r\n            </li>\r\n            <li><span class="block">Mobile Compatible</span>\r\n                Create and even edit your site on any mobile device seamlessly.\r\n            </li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="wp-host-cloud-features-wrp">\r\n    <div class="wp-host-features-content">\r\n        <h2><span class="prev"></span>Your WordPress Site - powered by our Cloud Hosting<span class="next"></span></h2>\r\n        <div class="block">\r\n            <div class="feature inline-block">\r\n                <span class="wp-host-feature-icon block fast"></span>\r\n                <h3>Blazing-Fast Load Time</h3>\r\n                <p>With top-of-the-line hardware and caching - which stores your site’s most used pages, and a globally\r\n                    distributed CDN, your site is served upto 2x faster.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class="feature inline-block last">\r\n                <span class="wp-host-feature-icon block scaling"></span>\r\n                <h3>Instant Scaling</h3>\r\n                <p>No need to move your hosting as your traffic grows. Ramp up your resources at the click of a button -\r\n                    instantly add RAM and CPU without a reboot.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class="block">\r\n            <div class="feature inline-block">\r\n                <span class="wp-host-feature-icon block safeguard"></span>\r\n                <h3>Your Data - Safeguarded</h3>\r\n                <p>Our industry-leading Ceph-based storage system stores your website data across 3 distinct devices to\r\n                    ensure redundancy and safety.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class="feature inline-block last">\r\n                <span class="wp-host-feature-icon block auto-fail"></span>\r\n                <h3>Automatic Failover</h3>\r\n                <p>If we detect a hardware issue, we automatically move your site to another server, ensuring that your\r\n                    site is always up and you never lose traffic.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n[vc_row][vc_column][vc_tta_accordion active_section="1" title="FAQs"][vc_tta_section title="Can I upgrade my WordPress Hosting plan?" tab_id="1597250051536-937007b7-8cdb"][vc_column_text]No, You cannot change upgrade or downgrade plans, however the amount of RAM and CPU cores for your plan can be upgraded.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I add more WordPress installations to an existing plan?" tab_id="1597250051543-62c91deb-0e0c"][vc_column_text]No, you cannot add more WordPress installations to any plan. The number of WordPress installations will remain fixed.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can SiteLock and CodeGuard packages be upgraded?" tab_id="1597250172987-3f71059c-db3a"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="faq">\r\n    <div class="answer">Currently, the included SiteLock and CodeGuard plans cannot be upgraded.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I use an external email service with WordPress Hosting?" tab_id="1597250237167-8132c4db-bb0b"][vc_column_text]Yes, you can use any 3rd party email service for your domain. In case you are using the default name servers provided with WordPress Hosting, please contact our Support team to update the relevant DNS records for your blog.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I use an existing certificate with my blog?" tab_id="1597250275291-c60b8fc5-d8b9"][vc_column_text]No, you cannot use an existing certificate. You will need to generate a CSR from the WordPress Hosting panel and get a certificate issued which can be installed from the panel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Will WordPress be updated automatically?" tab_id="1597250412214-b803d195-d0db"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="faq">\r\n    <div class="answer">Yes, WordPress core updates will be enabled by default.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Is there a money back period for WordPress Hosting?" tab_id="1597250447106-716329de-f756"][vc_column_text]No, WordPress Hosting does not have a money back period.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Is Multisite supported with WordPress Hosting?" tab_id="1597250488106-51245d39-6b27"][vc_column_text]No, Multisite is not supported.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Can I access the cPanel for my hosting plan?" tab_id="1597250526262-1dfb247d-f324"][vc_column_text]No, cPanel access is not provided with WordPress Hosting.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Is an SSL Certificate included with the plan?" tab_id="1597250567016-ad0f7e69-a6af"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="faq">\r\n    <div class="answer">Yes. When you purchase a WordPress Hosting order, Free SSL powered by Let\'s Encrypt, is\r\n        automatically generated and installed for all domains associated with the package\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="What is the difference between ``WordPress Hosting`` and ``WordPress Hosting + Security Suite`` plans?" tab_id="1597250604450-113bbabe-a105"][vc_column_text]WordPress Hosting plans are economical plans without automatic backups and anti-malware. WordPress Hosting + Security plans have the same specifications as that of the WordPress hosting plans, including automatic cloud backups and anti-malware at a cost difference.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'WordPress Hosting', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1124-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-08-13 17:02:29', '2020-08-13 17:02:29', '', 1124, 'http://redcirclehost.local/1124-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
